data.description:
Here's an invitation to a lifestyle of comfort, serenity, and community in the heart of Gold Canyon's Mountainbrook Village.
Step through the inviting front door and into the heart of this charming home. The Lantana floorplan welcomes you with its open layout, with the split bedrooms a perfect blend of comfort and perfect for visiting guests, adding to the comfort is NEW carpet underfoot, providing a cozy and fresh ambiance.
  As you stroll through the living room space, notice the wood-look tile adds a touch of warmth and durability. Continue your tour into the kitchen, seamlessly integrated into the open floor plan. The living space opens up to a private backyard oasis, backing to a wash for added tranquility and privacy. A wall of windows spans the back of the home, flooding the space with natural light and creating a seamless connection between indoor and outdoor living.
But this home is more than just a haven; it's part of Gold Canyon's premier active adult community in Mountainbrook Village. Enjoy the perks of community living with two heated pools and spa, a workout facility, and a community center/rec room for social gatherings. Stay active with pickleball courts and explore the myriad of other amenities that make this community a true gem.
